              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The 238U(n,f) reaction taken from IAEA Neutron Cross-",
                " section References (2015). Pronyaev V., Simakov S.,",
                " Marcinkevicius B., University of Leeds, 158, 80, 2015"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainties in the forward/backward cross",
                " section Sig(forward/backward) due to statistics,",
                " valid-event-area of alpha-source events, alpha",
                " particle detection efficiency, background reduction",
                " for the forward/backward events Err(forward/backward)",
                " is propagated to the corresponding uncertainty",
                " Err(total) in the total cross section Sig(tot) by",
                " Err(total)=sqrt((Sig(forward)*Err(forward))**2+",
                " (Sig(backward)*Err(backward))**2)/(Sig(forward)",
                " +(Sig(backward))",
                " Where the Sig(forward) are 0.1295 mb at 5.5 MeV,",
                " 0.3011 mb at 6.5 MeV; the Sig(backward) are",
                " 0.0636 mb at 5.5 MeV, 0.1117 mb at 6.5 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
